Yodle Ads Service Recurring Monthly Management Fee.   Customer agrees to pay a Monthly Management Fee of $20 per month until the Yodle Ads Service is cancelled.

Yodle Ads Service Term.  The term of the Yodle Ads Service is one (1) month and will automatically continue month to month thereafter (and Customer will be billed the applicable monthly fees on a monthly recurring basis), until the Yodle Ads Service is canceled.  Customer may pause the Yodle Ads Service at any time and will continue to be billed the Monthly Paid Media Management Fee for so long as the Yodle Ads Service remains paused.  Customer may cancel the Yodle Ads Service at any time, and (i) such cancellation will become effective at the end of the current billing cycle and (ii) Customer will not be billed any additional amounts for the Yodle Ads Service.

Customer accepts this Change Order, which is subject to the terms and conditions (http://www.yodle.com/legal/terms/master-subscription-agreement), by replying to this email with the words "I Accept" or similar language acknowledging assent.  This action creates an electronic signature that has the same legal force and effect as a handwritten signature on a written contract under any applicable law or regulation, and is equally binding.  This Change Order becomes effective on the date accepted by the Customer.

